5.3 Revisit the data example by using SAS
The court length data can be read by the following DATA step:
DATA TIME;
  INPUT TIME @@;
DATALINES;
43 90 84 87 116 95 86 99 93 92
121 71 66 98 79 102 60 112 105 98
